Passthrough flags (same in both CLIs):
  --model, --add-dir, --agent, --output-format, -p, -c, -v, --resume, etc.

cpc-specific flags:
  --help                               Show this help
  --dry-run                            Print translated command without running

Examples:
  cpc "explain this project"
    → copilot -i "explain this project"

